  m_text: "About Me:\n\nI love going on lake trips with my wife and dog, Koda. Every
    season you can find us at the lake swimming, skating, sailing, and more.\n\nPersonal
    Information:\n \tWorks at Shift Supervisor\n\tStudied at Bad Axe High School\n\tLives
    in Bad Axe, Michigan\n\tFrom Bad Axe, Michigan\n\tMarried to Lisa Bumpkin\n\n\tBirthday
